## How to Deploy and Run
1. Install base dependencies:
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
*(The `transformers` and `torch` libraries are already in requirements for the BERT deployment).*

2. Launch it via Waitress (Windows compatible production WSGI):
```bash
waitress-serve --port=5000 wsgi:app
```
*(First boot will dynamically cache the 500MB Transformer model, and it will be fast thereafter).*
